4 tests need fixing:

1. 'old extension WS is closed when a new connection arrives' (~line 236): ws created at ~line 249, closed at ~line 269. Wrap lines 262-275 (from waitForLog through waitForHealth) in try/finally with ws.close() in finally.

2. 'ping/pong keepalive works' (~line 278): ws created at ~line 287, closed at ~line 321. Wrap lines 300-319 (pongPromise setup through expect) in try/finally.

